overview.en: Universal exchange is a decentralized autonomous organization structured on top of Aragon DAO. Our team is made up of like-minded individuals who are motivated to leverage blockchain technology to improve the existing workflows of traditional financial services.
overview.zh: Ue 是一个由志同道合的技术和金融极客组成的，构建在Aragon 上的去中心化开发组织。我们聚焦开发区块链金融的基础设施项目，旨在利用区块链技术改善传统金融服务的流程。
